Package rekit.logic.level

Class Level

java.lang.Object
rekit.logic.level.Level
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Level>, DataKeySetter
public final class Level
extends Object
implements Comparable<Level>, DataKeySetter
This class represents a Level for a ILevelScene with its StructurePart and LogicalPart.

Dominik Fuchss
